{"tha-ap504:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap504:0.2":"Kanikaravagga ","tha-ap504:0.3":"Ekapattadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap504:1.1":"“Nagare hamsavatiya, ","tha-ap504:1.2":"kumbhakaro ahosaham; ","tha-ap504:1.3":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap504:1.4":"oghatinnamanasavam. ","tha-ap504:2.1":"Sukatam mattikapattam, ","tha-ap504:2.2":"buddhasetthassadasaham; ","tha-ap504:2.3":"Pattam datva bhagavato, ","tha-ap504:2.4":"ujubhutassa tadino. ","tha-ap504:3.1":"Bhave nibbattamanoham, ","tha-ap504:3.2":"sonnathale labhamaham; ","tha-ap504:3.3":"Rupimaye ca sovanne, ","tha-ap504:3.4":"tattike ca manimaye. ","tha-ap504:4.1":"Patiyo paribhunjami, ","tha-ap504:4.2":"punnakammassidam phalam; ","tha-ap504:4.3":"Yasananca dhanananca, ","tha-ap504:4.4":"aggabhuto ca homaham. ","tha-ap504:5.1":"Yathapi bhaddake khette, ","tha-ap504:5.2":"bijam appampi ropitam; ","tha-ap504:5.3":"Sammadharam pavecchante, ","tha-ap504:5.4":"phalam toseti kassakam. ","tha-ap504:6.1":"Tathevidam pattadanam, ","tha-ap504:6.2":"buddhakhettamhi ropitam; ","tha-ap504:6.3":"Pitidhare pavassante, ","tha-ap504:6.4":"phalam mam tosayissati. ","tha-ap504:7.1":"Yavata khetta vijjanti, ","tha-ap504:7.2":"sanghapi ca ganapi ca; ","tha-ap504:7.3":"Buddhakhettasamo natthi, ","tha-ap504:7.4":"sukhado sabbapaninam. ","tha-ap504:8.1":"Namo te purisajanna, ","tha-ap504:8.2":"namo te purisuttama; ","tha-ap504:8.3":"Ekapattam daditvana, ","tha-ap504:8.4":"pattomhi acalam padam. ","tha-ap504:9.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap504:9.2":"yam pattamadadim tada; ","tha-ap504:9.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap504:9.4":"pattadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap504:10.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap504:10.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap504:10.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap504:11.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap504:11.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap504:11.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap504:12.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap504:12.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap504:12.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap504:13.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ekapattadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap504:14.1":"Ekapattadayakattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}